cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.MM

This paper is about improving the quality and speed of optical flow estimation using deep learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), which focuses on image and video analysis. The paper also discusses the importance of training data and the use of stacked architectures, which are topics related to machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG and cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of optical flow in robotics (cs.RO) and multimedia applications (cs.MM), which are also possible categories.
